eratur- und Kulturwissenschaft gleichermaßen geöffnet.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4a19. Jahrhundert. 4aAlberdis. 4aEcheverría. 4aGeneración Del 37. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aLateinamerika. 4aLiberalismus. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aMitre. 4aMármol. 4aNation Building. 4aNation. 4aRomanistik. 4aSarmiento. 4aSpanische Literatur. 4aSüdamerikanische Geschichte. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / Spanish & Portuguese.2bisacsh  a19th Century.  aAlberdis.  aCultural History.  aEcheverría.  aGeneración Del 37.  aLatin America.  aLiberalism.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aMitre.  aMármol.  aNation Building.  aNation.  aRomance Studies.  aSarmiento.  aSouth American History.  aSpanish Literature.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2017z978311071954308iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2018z9783110603187oZDB-23-DKU40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839440001zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839440001423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839440001/original  a978-3-11-071954-3  DG Plus eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DKUb2018